Data:
[ Commonwealth Act No. 29, September 08, 1936 ]
AN ACT CHANGING THE NAME OF THE BARRIO OF GUMALPONG. MUNICIPALITY OF BACO, PROVINCE OF MINDORO, TO THAT OF SANTA ROSA.(awÞhi(
Be it enacted by the National Assembly of the Philippines:
Section 1. The name of the barrio of Gumalpong, municipality of Baco, Province of Mindoro, is hereby changed to that of Santa Rosa.
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Enacted, without Executive approval, September 8, 1936.
